reviewText: This version is the Best of them All ... Loved it then, love it more now ... A TREASURE

This DVD is the 1970 version, not the 1968.  The picture is right, the description is wrong. This is the 1970 movie starring Dinah Sheridan, Jenny Agutter and Bernard Cribbins, not the 1968 TV series starring Jenny Agutter, Gillian Bailey, Ann Castle, Gordon Gostelow, Neil McDermott.
